{
  "text": "The Alpha-defensin test already shows its reliability regardless preceding antibiotic treatment [CITATION_1] . Our data is consistent with this evidence and demonstrated that Synovasure\u2122 is a reliable test even in presence of blood contamination of SF samples. The relatively high percentage (13.4%) of patients under antibiotic therapy started before referral to a specialized hospital, highlight the need of educational improvement of primary care providers who deal with patients with painful joint arthroplasty [CITATION_2] .",
